
This disk contains the source code and make file
for the complete C Image Processing System
as described in 8 articles in the C Users Journal.


All source code and the makefile for C Image
Processing System are in the \code directory.

The root directory contains documentation files
generated by the C-DOC commercial product.  These
files give a table of contents of functions, a 
function hierarchy tree, and the called and calling
functions.
